ajana: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Sprinttien jrjestminen tyryhmlle.</li><li>Tyryhmn jsenten potentiaalin realisoiminen hyvll johtamisella.</li><li>Jira:n kyttminen.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>Kielitaito:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>Englanti</strong><ul><li>idinkieli.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Suomi</strong><ul><li>Luksia Oy:n suomen kielen keskitason tutkinnon (2019):<ul><li>Puheen ymmrtminen: 4/4</li><li>Puhuminen: 4/4</li><li>Tekstin ymmrtminen: 4/4</li><li>Kirjoittaminen: 3/4</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>Koulutus:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>Maalis 2021  viel jatkuu (2023):</strong></td><td>Taitotalo, Helsinki. Tieto- ja viestinttekniikan<br>tutkinto, Ohjelmistokehittj</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":74,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://davittb.nube.taitotalo-ict.fi/davitt-portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/davitts_album_no3_FULLRES_4000x4000-e1654064680492-1024x243.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->", "Profiili", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "23-revision-v1", "", "", "2022-07-04 08:54:35", "2022-07-04 05:54:35", "", "23", "https://davittb.nube.taitotalo-ict.fi/davitt-portfolio/?p=183", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `dp_posts` VALUES("184", "1", "2022-07-04 08:55:12", "2022-07-04 05:55:12", "<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>About me:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I moved to Finland from Dublin, Ireland in 2011 with the intention of expanding my music career in a country I love very much. I achieved in my goals of becoming a completely self-employed musician and music producer for over 10 years in Finland and countries across Europe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since covid hit, I have been moving back to my original favorite interest which is ICT and programming. My most recent job was with CGI as a Service Desk Specialist (2022). Now, I am a student with Taitotalo studying in Information Communications Technology and Programming. I am to complete the studies around spring 2023.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>IT skills:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Programming languages:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>HTML</li><li>JavaScript (React)</li><li>Node.js</li><li>Express.js</li><li>CSS</li><li>Bootstrap</li><li>PHP</li><li>MySQL</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>GitHub pages:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><a href=\"https://github.com/DavittBarry/ruokatori\">https://github.com/DavittBarry/ruokatori</a></li><li><a href=\"https://github.com/EdvardJ/PlantPlanner\">https://github.com/EdvardJ/PlantPlanner</a></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>General:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Installation of many different operating systems and applications.</li><li>Installing printing and scanning machines.</li><li>Managing user accounts in Active directory and other administrative tools.</li><li>Website designing.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Computer construction:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Building new computer systems.</li><li>Modification of prebuilt computers systems.</li><li>Integrate hardware from redundant systems into other PCs.</li><li>Component error troubleshooting.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Networking:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>General Setup of Networks.</li><li>Constructing Cat5 (RJ45) Cables.</li><li>Structured Cabling.</li><li>Installing Switches &amp; Hubs.</li><li>Creating user accounts on a network.</li><li>Updating Operating Systems.</li><li>Hardware Troubleshooting.</li><li>Troubleshooting and resolving network Printer issues.</li><li>Wireless connection setup and configuration.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Applications:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Excel using Pivot tables, generating reports etc.</li><li>Proficient in using Microsoft Outlook, Word and SharePoint.</li><li>High level of skill in ticket systems such as: ServiceNow, OVSD and OVSC.</li><li>Remote tools such as Windows Remote Desktop, Bomgar, Citrix, VNC ja NetMeeting.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Agile Product Owner skills:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Organizing sprints for the team.</li><li>Facilitating teammates so they reach their max potential.</li><li>Usage of systems such as Jira for team and product organizing.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>Language skills:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>English</strong><ul><li>Mother tongue.</li></ul></li><li><strong>Finnish</strong><ul><li>Luksia Oy Finnish language average level exam (2019):<ul><li><strong>Understanding speech: 4/4</strong></li><li><strong>Speaking: 4/4</strong></li><li><strong>Understanding text: 4/4</strong></li><li><strong>Writing: 3/4&nbsp;</strong></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"fontSize\":\"x-large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-x-large-font-size\"><strong>Further education:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>March 2021  In progress (2023)</strong>:</td><td>Taitotalo, Helsinki. Information and Communication Technology, Software Developer.</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":74,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"https://davittb.nube.taitotalo-ict.fi/davitt-portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/davitts_album_no3_FULLRES_4000x4000-e1654064680492-1024x243.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->", "Profile", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "19-revision-v1", "", "", "2022-07-04 08:55:12", "2022-07-04 05:55:12", "", "19", "https://davittb.nube.taitotalo-ict.fi/davitt-portfolio/?p=184", "0", "revision", "", "0");
